---
// Privacy notice (Datenschutzerklärung). Reflects how the site actually works:
// static hosting on Cloudflare Pages, cookieless Cloudflare Web Analytics,
// self-hosted fonts, no cookies, no advertising or cross-site tracking.
// Fill in the [placeholder] and have the final text reviewed by a professional —
// this is a starting template, not legal advice.
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy — Sergey Völker"
  description="How personal data is handled on sergeyvoelker.com."
>
  <article class="pt-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight">Privacy</h1>
    <div class="prose mt-8">
      <p>
        This notice explains how personal data is handled when you visit
        <strong>sergeyvoelker.com</strong>. This site is intentionally minimal:
        it sets no cookies, shows no advertising, and does not track you across
        other websites.
      </p>

      <h2>Who is responsible</h2>
      <p>
        The controller responsible for data processing on this website is Sergey
        Völker. Full contact details are in the <a href="/impressum">Impressum</a>.
        For any data-protection request, use the contact address given there.
      </p>

      <h2>Hosting and server logs</h2>
      <p>
        This site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. When you open a page, Cloudflare
        automatically processes the technical data needed to deliver the site and
        keep it secure — including your IP address, the page requested, the date
        and time, the referring page, and your browser type. This is based on our
        legitimate interest in running a secure, functioning website
        (Art. 6 (1) (f) GDPR). Cloudflare acts as our processor and may process
        data on infrastructure operated by Cloudflare, Inc. under EU-approved
        safeguards (Standard Contractual Clauses).
      </p>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        To understand which pages are read, we use Cloudflare Web Analytics. It is
        privacy-focused: it uses <strong>no cookies</strong>, does not fingerprint
        visitors, and collects only aggregated, non-identifying figures such as
        page views, referrers, country, and device type. No profile about you is
        created. Legal basis: legitimate interest (Art. 6 (1) (f) GDPR).
      </p>

      <h2>Fonts</h2>
      <p>
        All fonts are hosted directly on this site. No data is sent to Google
        Fonts or other third parties to display text.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This site sets no cookies and uses no local storage for tracking. For that
        reason, no cookie banner is shown.
      </p>

      <h2>External links</h2>
      <p>
        This site links to external services such as LinkedIn, Medium, and Amazon.
        When you follow such a link, the privacy policy of that provider applies;
        we have no influence over how they process your data.
      </p>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>
        Under the GDPR you have the right to access (Art. 15), rectification
        (Art. 16), erasure (Art. 17), restriction of processing (Art. 18), data
        portability (Art. 20), and to object to processing (Art. 21). You also have
        the right to lodge a complaint with a data-protection supervisory
        authority.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to this notice</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this notice as the site evolves. The version published here
        always applies.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
